Title: Wilo Yonos Maxo-D 40/0.5-8 PN6/10 twin head commercial pump
Description: The Wilo Yonos Maxo-D is a twin head compact pump for commercial buildings with HVAC applications, with an EC motor and electronic power adjustment for optimum energy efficiency.  Easy to set up with three operating modes and simple adjustment over three speed stages when replacing an uncontrolled standard pump. Additional option to expand the pumps intelligent functions further with the Wilo Connect Module.   Each pump operates individually with one main pump and one pump on standby, meaning if any faults are detected you can switch the pumps over to prevent failure.  This inline glandless pump is suitable for use in domestic or commercial buildings for all central heating, underfloor heating, air-conditioning systems, closed cooling circuits, industrial circulation systems.
